Dr. Seecoomar is one of the most caring doctors I have ever met. He is also one of the most intelligent doctors I have met, at least from a patients point of view.
Thanks for all your help.  I hope to not have to see you for medical reasons, but maybe for fun.  If I can ever help you with real estate needs I will be more than happy to help.
